answers: The New Jersey Juror Questionnaire can be filled out electronically through the Court’s website eResponse and if you have questions related to jury service you may review the court Frequently Asked Questions page Frequently Asked Questions About Jury Service or you may contact your local Jury Manager Jury Management Office Contact List for assistance.
